You are working on the Octopus Transportation Management System (TMS) project.

Key reminders:
- Use Java 21 with Spring Boot 3.5.1
- Frontend uses React 19.1 with TypeScript, Webpack 5, and Tailwind CSS
- NO DOCKER - Local PostgreSQL 14 on port 5432
- NO FLYWAY temporarily - migrations disabled
- Multi-module Gradle structure (base, core, load, broker, shipper, carrier, financial, web)
- Run frontend: npm run devserver (port 3000)
- Run backend: ./gradlew bootRun -Dspring.profiles.active=local
- Test with: ./gradlew test and npm run test
- E2E testing with Playwright: npm run test:e2e
- Screenshot generation with Puppeteer: npm run screenshots
- Focus on completing Broker module first
- Authentication uses JWT with role hierarchy
- Always check CLAUDE.md for project conventions
- Database: octopus-tms-b, user: haydarovbahtiyar, password: password